---
title: Roasted Cauliflower & Israeli Couscous Salad with Crumbly Cheese, Toasted Almonds & Smokey Aioli
description: We love the tender texture of Israeli couscous, each grain holds its shape and easily handles bold flavours. Combine that with
spiced roasted veggies, crumbly cheese and crisp salad leaves for a salad to remember!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-cauliflower-goat-cheese-salad-7070305b.jpg
